snippet.title: A Webbing Journey - April 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play a cute little spider in this innovative and wholesome 3D puzzle platformer where you explore lush and stunning islands on your quest to collect the most exotic flowers for your spider date.

Become a web designer, swing around, make new friends, and solve quests and mysterious puzzles during your journey.

This trailer is representing the current development stage of our game. Everything seen in it is subject to change.

Play the demo and wishlist our game on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2073910/A_Webbing_Journey/

Check out our website for more information
https://www.firetotemgames.com/

And follow us on Twitter for updates about the game
https://twitter.com/FireTotemGames
